TsoSampleAnalysisResultsFile R6 Class

Source: R/tso.R
TsoSampleAnalysisResultsFile.Rd

Contains methods for reading and displaying contents of the SampleAnalysisResults.json.gz file output from TSO.

Super class

Method read()

Reads the SampleAnalysisResults.json.gz file output from TSO.

Usage

TsoSampleAnalysisResultsFile$read()

Returns

list of tibbles

Method clone()

The objects of this class are cloneable with this method.

Usage

TsoSampleAnalysisResultsFile$clone(deep = FALSE)

Arguments

deep

Whether to make a deep clone.

Examples

x <- system.file("extdata/tso/sample705_SampleAnalysisResults.json.gz", package = "dracarys")
res <- TsoSampleAnalysisResultsFile$new(x)
res$read() # or read(res)
